    "faq_with_image_m73Xra": {
      "type": "faq-with-image",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_GhRGXt": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "How can I commission a bespoke ring design that perfectly captures my unique aesthetic?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>A commitment ring, engagement band, or statement piece should feel intrinsically 'you.' We guide clients through the initial concepts, working with sketches and moulds to ensure every curve and setting is uniquely designed by hand within our workshop. </p><p>To begin this deeply personal journey toward realising your bespoke vision in ring form, an appointment at our Showroom is essential for any client based in {{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.location.value }}.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_HmVJLJ": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Do you provide guidance on choosing the right metal (Platinum vs. Gold) for a ring designed to be worn every day?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>The choice of metal heavily influences both longevity and wearability. Platinum offers exceptional durability while maintaining its lustre, whereas various grades of gold offer unique warmth and colour tones suitable for diverse skin types and tastes. </p><p>Our master goldsmiths are adept at advising on which material possesses the optimal balance of resilience and beauty required for daily life near {{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.location.value }}. We recommend a private consultation to compare samples before committing to your design.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_xFhTbU": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "If I am replacing an older ring, how can you ensure the restoration maintains its original integrity while modernising it?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>We approach jewellery remodelling as an act of conservation and reimagining. Our artisans are meticulous in assessing vintage rings—whether they bear a significant family legacy or simply require structural reinforcement. </p><p>The preservation work takes place right here at our secure Chichester workshop, guaranteeing that the unique history and artisanal detail remain utterly undisturbed while adding modern refinement relevant to your life in {{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.location.value }}.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_pxHnfz": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "What guidance do you offer regarding sizing, especially if I am travelling or changing rings often?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Ring sizing is perhaps the most delicate aspect of bespoke jewellery. Precision is paramount, as a millimetre makes all the difference in fit and comfort. We conduct thorough, measured fittings—which are vastly superior to estimation techniques. </p><p>To guarantee flawless accuracy for your purchase whether you are from {{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.location.value }} or are passing through Chichester, we strongly advise booking an appointment at our Showroom.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_BRezAN": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Can my new ring incorporate materials that relate specifically to the history or motifs of West Sussex/Hampshire?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Absolutely; your ring can become a wearable piece of local art and natural heritage. We specialise in drawing inspiration from regional iconography—be it subtle botanical details, historical architecture, or raw material sources prevalent near {{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.location.value }}. </p><p>During a private consultation at our Showroom, we can review examples of work that successfully fuse your personal narrative with meaningful regional artistic motifs.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
